<li><a href="Tajikistan" title="Tajikistan">Tajikistan</a>: Persian</li>
<li><a href="Thailand" title="Thailand">Thailand</a>: Thai</li>
<li><a href="Turkey" title="Turkey">Turkey</a>: Turkish</li>
